Class ProfileCreationWindow

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.googlecode.lanterna.gui.Window
      • capstone.ui.Widget
        • capstone.ui.ProfileCreationWindow
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.googlecode.lanterna.gui.Component

    public class ProfileCreationWindow
extends Widget
    The Window for creating a profile. A profile can be created from an ID, a real name, a Representation and a KeyMap.

      • _createBottomButtons

        protected void _createBottomButtons()
        Create the buttons at the bottom of the window. Those buttons are a button to create the profile (which also validates the input), then a button to cancel the creation and lastly a button to exit the program.

      • _createCreateButton
